name: Genevieve_Double_Door_Wall_Cabinet_by_Elegant_Home_Fashions
reviews: Better than the picture! Works very good in my bathroom Purchased the floor cabinet to. Store all my Towels and bath mats in both the WALL and FLOOR cabinets.

Arrived with several scratches which I was willing to overlook if I was able to buff them out, but then when I went to put it together, one of the pieces didn't have the drill holes like the instructions indicated. Avoid at all costs!
